ongoing development activities of her government.
</P>
<P>
Listing various development activities of the government, the
prime minister said the objective of her government is to improve
the quality of life of the common man.
</P>
<P>
Sheikh Hasina returned to the capital Saturday evening on
conclusion of her two-day visit to her home town.
</P>
