imprisonment on a charge of tax evasion and disqualified him from
holding any public office for 21 years.
</P>
<P>
Sharif, who is already serving two concurrent life terms on
charge of hijacking and terrorism, also was fined 20 million
rupees (37,000 U.S. dollars). (Pakistan-Sharif)
</P>
