Li Hongzhi, has came out from behind the curtain to publish his
instructions via the Internet and repeatedly spelt out his
hackneyed remark about the "final chance for 'consummation'" to
urge his followers to come out "against the pressure", and risk
direct confrontation with the government.
</P>
